I"Ž<p>The trick is to select the first child when itâ€™s also the nth-from-the-last child. This effectively selects based on the number of siblings.</p>

<p>The key part is the following</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    li:first-child:nth-last-child(2),
    li:first-child:nth-last-child(2) ~ li {
        width: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00C9FF 0%, #92FE9D 100%);
    }
</code></pre></div></div>

